    'legal.privacy.section2.content': 'To ensure adequate protection of company and client data, we implement all required organizational and technical measures as stipulated by the Personal Data Protection Act. We have established rules to prevent data breaches and misuse, supporting secure processing and safeguarding of your data. For maximum security during processing, transfer, and storage, we may use additional protection mechanisms such as encryption and pseudonymization.',
    'legal.privacy.section3.title': '3. Users\' Rights',
