    'legal.cookies.section1.title': '1. How Are Cookies Used on This Website?',
    'legal.cookies.section1.content': 'We use cookies primarily to enhance site usability, improve website performance, and store information about user behavior. No personal data is stored through cookies; therefore, users cannot be personally identified, and data protection laws do not apply to this information. The data collected by cookies is generally aggregated to analyze user behavior on the website, allowing us to improve site functionality, user journeys, and content. Cookies may also be used for direct marketing purposes, such as delivering electronic commercial messages to users outside the website.',
    'legal.cookies.section2.title': '2. What Types of Cookies Are Used on This Website?',
    'legal.cookies.section2.subsection1.title': '2.1 Session Cookies',
    'legal.cookies.section2.subsection1.content': 'These cookies facilitate site usage by temporarily storing information during the browser session only. Typically, they store data such as items added to a shopping cart, pages visited, and navigation paths. Session cookies do not collect information from your device and are deleted automatically when you leave the site or close your browser session.',
    'legal.cookies.section2.subsection2.title': '2.2 Persistent Cookies',
    'legal.cookies.section2.subsection2.content': 'These cookies allow us to store specific browsing information, such as analyzing site visits, how users reached the site, which pages were viewed, options selected, and navigation paths taken through the website. Tracking this information enables us to make website improvements, fix errors, and expand content. The duration of storage for persistent cookies varies depending on their specific purpose.',
